This has to be the best start of a year for me! I’m happy to announce that I signed a distribution deal with @chillselect to release my new upcoming EP “Reflections of HE” on their label. I’ve worked with them before on singles that ended up on a few of their compilation beat tapes, but never as a body of work! This will be my debut on the record label and the first single “Shipping (Out)” will be available March 3rd and the whole EP will be available on March 24th!
